(12111, 'Vastaflam 50mg 20 sugar coated tab.', 'فاستافلام 50مجم 20 قرص', '23', '36', 'Diclofenac potassium', 'Eipico', 'Tab', 'أقراص', '2- المثيل المكافيء تماما لأقراص كتافلام', 'Nsaid.acetic acid derivatives', '50mg', 'Diclofenac is indicated for use in the treatment of pain and inflammation from varying sources including inflammatory conditions such as osteoarthritis, rheumatoid arthritis, and ankylosing spondylitis, as well as injury-related inflammation due to surgery and physical trauma. It is often used in combination with [misoprostol] as a gastro-protective agent in patients with high risk of developing NSAID-induced ulcers.', '6221032118950', '', 18360, '2024-07-09', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
