(21773, 'Levotavin 750 mg 7 f.c.tabs.', 'ليفوتافين 750مجم 7 قرص', '75', '108', 'Levofloxacin', 'Pharco', 'Tab', 'أقراص', 'مضاد حيوي', 'Antibiotic.quinolone', '750 mg', 'In oral and intravenous formulations, levofloxacin is indicated in adults for the treatment of various infections caused by susceptible bacteria, including infections of the upper respiratory tract, lower respiratory tract, skin, skin structures, urinary tract, and prostate.[L11638,L11692] The oral formulation is also indicated in both adults and children 6 months of age and older for the post-exposure management of inhalational anthrax caused by _Bacillus anthracis_ and for the treatment and/or prophylaxis of plague caused by _Yersinia pestis_.[L11638]
In its ophthalmic formulation, levofloxacin is indicated for the treatment of bacterial conjunctivitis caused by susceptible organisms.[L11641] An inhalational solution available in Canada is indicated for the management of cystic fibrosis patients aged 18 years or older with chronic pulmonary _Pseudomonas aeruginosa_ infections.[L11689]', '6221151003779', '', 9915, '2024-09-05', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
